1. When the user clicks the link, the system shall download the executable
2. When the user clicks the downloaded executable, the system will execute the file
3. When the user clicks new game, the system will initialize a new game
4. When the user selects a ship from the initial pool, the system will detract that ship from the pool
5. When the user drags the ship to the field, the system will add it to the field
6. When the user has dragged all ships to the field, the system will prompt the user to verify the selection and placement of ships
7. When the user verifies the selection and placement of ships, the system will randomly determine who goes first (player or AI)
8. When the user selects an enemy potion to fire at, the system will determine if it is a hit or a miss and check if all ships are sunk
9. When the user has finished is his turn (after firing at enemy position), the system will the AI to take its turn and check if all ships are sunk
10. When the user has either won or lost, the system declars the winner and goes back to main menu
